  "detailed_description": "Paws for Adventure is a retro styled adventure game inspired by old school Zelda games but with cats.<br>Play the part of Cocoa a black cat who gets separated from his owners and ends up living with wild cats in the forest. Legend, action and adventures await as Cocoa fights, sings and hunts his way through the land.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996360/extras/5fc6e1d3e465671675ce8eac86a09057.poster.avif?t=1726251351\" width=400 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996360/extras/5fc6e1d3e465671675ce8eac86a09057.webm?t=1726251351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Hunt prey for food. Each animal gives different boosts to stats so keep an eye out for the more elusive prey. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996360/extras/39ac9d019e109bce08c53699bad8cf16.apng?t=1726251351\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996360/extras/39ac9d019e109bce08c53699bad8cf16.poster.avif?t=1726251351\" class=\"bb_img\" width=400 height=64 /></picture></span><br>Sleep at the graves of past cats. Cats who have passed on may have important skills to teach you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996360/extras/d0be441435c5d2045c7e0048c5590c7d.webp?t=1726251351\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996360/extras/d0be441435c5d2045c7e0048c5590c7d.poster.avif?t=1726251351\" class=\"bb_img\" width=400 height=128 /></picture></span><br>Meow magical melodies. Different songs will have different effects on yourself or the world around you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1996360/extras/60d04913a4b3c1a733ffc8554d83fdc2.avif?t=1726251351\" width=640 height=90 /></span><br>Explore The forest, dungeons, caves, canyons, beaches and more in your quest to save the cat colonies.",
